name: Whisper Drip
texteffect: Exhaust: Roll and place a xxMAGIC at this location.

name: Wound Paste
texteffect: Exhaust: All characters at location recover 1 xxBODY.

name: Loomwood Apples
texteffect: Exhaust: All characters at location gain 1 xxAP.

name: Wobbly Naz
texteffect: Holds xxRESOURCExxRESOURCE. Spend 1xxAP to place xxRESOURCE onto camel. May freely move xxRESOURCE from camel to character's location.

name: Traveling Tent
texteffect: Exhaust: Spend a xxTECHNOLOGY at this location to give all characters at location 1xxINITIATIVE.

name: Book of Pressed Leaves
texteffect: Exhaust: Place a xxPROGRESS on a xxLORE obstacle at this location.

name: Thieves' Tools
texteffect: Exhaust: Place a xxPROGRESS on an xxEDGE obstacle at this location.

name: Stoutleaf Blade Polish
texteffect: Exhaust: Place a xxPROGRESS on any Foe obstacle at this location.

name: Zarrah's Charm
texteffect: Exhaust: Refresh an xxABILITY card.

name: Azadeh
texteffect: Exhaust: Trade a xxDIPLOMACY at this location for xxSTABILITY of same value.

name: Windillipus Featherton
texteffect: Exhaust: Gain 1 xxMOVE.

name: Yasmina
texteffect: Exhaust: Cancel one stress from xxMAGIC backlash at this location.

name: Pox Face
texteffect: Exhaust: Move a Companion or Diplomat from xxASSET staging area to crafting area.

name: Mad Honey
texteffect: Exhaust: Lose 1 xxPSYCHE to gain 1 xxINITIATIVE.

name: Mask of the Frenzied Beast
texteffect: Exhaust: Lose 1 xxPSYCHE to ignore all xxBODY dice during an overcome action.

name: Murjan
texteffect: Exhaust: Place a xxPROGRESS on a xxSTEEL obstacle at this location.

name: Dragon of the Critical Word
texteffect: Exhaust: Lose 2 xxPSYCHE to discard any Foe in play (from any location).

name: The Icon of Channeling
texteffect: Exhaust: Convert all xxHINDRANCE to xxPROGRESS on a xxLORE obstacle at this location.

name: Zeno the Squidmonger
texteffect: Exhaust: Place a xxPROGRESS on a Spy or Guard at this location.

name: Master of Coin
texteffect: Exhaust: If at an xxEMPIRE location, draw an xxABILITY card.

name: Zarrah
texteffect: Exhaust: Spend 2 xxDIPLOMACY at this location to discard any Diplomat in play (from any location).

name: Delir
texteffect: Exhaust: Trade a xxMILITARY at this location of value xxFIVE for 2 xxMILITARY each with value xxTHREE.

name: Mirror of Melting
texteffect: Exhaust: Roll stress dice before allocating xxDEFENSE when overcoming a Unit.

name: Hogel
texteffect: Exhaust: Convert all xxHINDRANCE to xxPROGRESS on a xxCHARM obstacle at this location.

name: Pin of the Plum
texteffect: Exhaust: Move to any Tavern or Winehouse.

name: Pearlescent Lotus
texteffect: Exhaust: Lose 1 xxBODY to place xxPROGRESSxxPROGRESS on a xxLORE obstacle at this location.

name: Gelshah's Heart
texteffect: Gain an extra xxINITIATIVE during refresh phase. If any xxINITIATIVE roll a xxSIX during refresh, lose 1 xxPSYCHE.

name: Dragon of the Frozen Voice
texteffect: Exhaust: Place a xxPROGRESS on an Issue at this location.

name: The Uncut String
texteffect: Exhaust: After rolling for a condition, may set one die to any value.

name: Shelly the Flying Turtle
texteffect: Shelley has an independent xxMOVEMENT of 2. During refresh, may swap places with Shelley.

name: Love Letter
texteffect: xxPLAY on another character or diplomat to gain the IN LOVE WITH reserve action.

name: Baklava
texteffect: xxPLAY: recover one xxBODY. May not increase die past xxSIX.

name: Travel Pack
texteffect: May transport xxRESOURCE die.

name: Ilya the Captain
texteffect: Costs 1 xxMOVE to move between xxPORT locations.

name: Forest Yoga
texteffect: xxPLAY: recover 2 xxPSYCHE. May not increase die past xxSIX.

name: Gelshah's Map
texteffect: xxPLAY at any Eldritch location to add Eldritch location to xxBRIGHTDUNE or xxSETTLED.

name: Ley Line Map
texteffect: xxPLAY at any xxSETTLED Wilderness location to add Wilderness location to xxSETTLED.

name: Gurgle Gut
texteffect: xxPLAY: discard one diplomat at this location.

name: Eliza's Mirror
texteffect: During Refresh, take 2 xxBODY. xxUPGRADE costs one less die.

name: Basket of Arrows
texteffect: Ancient method for counting the war dead. Could also be an obstacle or scene title.
